WEBVTT

00:00:42.520 --> 00:00:43.880
I know you're twisted

00:00:44.920 --> 00:00:47.399
I know you enjoy watching others suffer

00:00:49.759 --> 00:00:50.439
But

00:00:51.600 --> 00:00:53.520
I'm the one who destroyed you

00:00:55.240 --> 00:00:56.679
And I feel great too

00:00:57.520 --> 00:00:58.000
You...

00:02:43.240 --> 00:02:44.639
The police have decrypted the USB drive

00:02:45.759 --> 00:02:46.879
Inside, there are years of

00:02:47.360 --> 00:02:49.319
evidence of Jiang Nanshuo's illegal businesses

00:02:50.479 --> 00:02:52.039
Enough to make him rot in jail

00:03:07.919 --> 00:03:08.879
I understand

00:03:09.520 --> 00:03:09.960
Also

00:03:11.039 --> 00:03:12.560
the accidental fire case from ten years ago

00:03:13.319 --> 00:03:14.719
will also be reinvestigated

00:03:15.680 --> 00:03:17.400
Have you thought about taking this chance

00:03:19.639 --> 00:03:21.280
Long Weiwei is dead

00:03:23.439 --> 00:03:24.520
It's all over

00:03:25.039 --> 00:03:25.719
Hei Ba

00:03:29.120 --> 00:03:30.000
Call me Cheng Ye

00:04:24.959 --> 00:04:25.639
Yi Xin

00:04:32.560 --> 00:04:33.240
Why is it you

00:04:39.519 --> 00:04:41.639
Did a pipe burst at your place

00:04:42.160 --> 00:04:42.839
No

00:04:43.399 --> 00:04:43.920
I...

00:04:44.040 --> 00:04:44.720
was just taking a shower

00:04:49.279 --> 00:04:50.439
Just wait a moment

00:04:51.600 --> 00:04:52.519
Don't go, don't go, don't go

00:04:54.920 --> 00:04:55.560
What are you doing

00:04:56.319 --> 00:04:57.839
I've been your fan for ten years

00:04:59.560 --> 00:05:01.160
Just be mine

00:05:03.560 --> 00:05:04.199
Are you okay

00:05:05.199 --> 00:05:05.600
I...

00:05:06.079 --> 00:05:06.759
You've got issues

00:05:08.240 --> 00:05:09.240
I like you

00:05:11.279 --> 00:05:12.439
Can you...

00:05:12.959 --> 00:05:14.399
give me a chance

00:05:28.360 --> 00:05:29.759
Damn Hei Ba

00:05:30.560 --> 00:05:31.879
Stinking Hei Ba

00:05:33.240 --> 00:05:35.000
And to think I liked you so much

00:05:38.800 --> 00:05:39.199
Hey, beauty

00:05:39.360 --> 00:05:40.079
Need a coach

00:05:42.920 --> 00:05:43.680
Let's race

00:05:56.160 --> 00:05:57.319
Stinking Hei Ba

00:05:58.160 --> 00:06:00.360
How dare you reject me

00:06:01.279 --> 00:06:03.120
I don't believe I can't win you over

00:06:36.959 --> 00:06:38.199
What are you doing here?

00:06:40.959 --> 00:06:41.759
I came to clear my mind.

00:06:43.079 --> 00:06:43.600
Oh.

00:06:45.160 --> 00:06:45.879
What's wrong?

00:06:46.519 --> 00:06:48.360
Is the young lady in a bad mood?

00:06:49.199 --> 00:06:50.800
I just went through a breakup.

00:06:51.800 --> 00:06:52.360
Let's go.

00:06:53.399 --> 00:06:54.399
Have a drink with me.

00:06:59.240 --> 00:06:59.920
Cheers.

00:07:03.120 --> 00:07:04.639
I'm the one who's heartbroken.

00:07:05.240 --> 00:07:06.639
You didn't get dumped.

00:07:07.160 --> 00:07:08.439
Why do you need to clear your mind?

00:07:11.759 --> 00:07:12.759
All these years...

00:07:14.240 --> 00:07:15.079
I thought I had already...

00:07:15.079 --> 00:07:16.439
...gotten used to living alone.

00:07:17.199 --> 00:07:17.839
I didn't expect...

00:07:18.720 --> 00:07:19.839
...that from start to finish...

00:07:20.800 --> 00:07:22.000
...it was just self-deception.

00:07:22.879 --> 00:07:24.040
As soon as he appears...

00:07:25.079 --> 00:07:26.879
...he disrupts everything I've faked.

00:07:28.480 --> 00:07:30.319
Those years by Jiang Nanshuo's side...

00:07:31.240 --> 00:07:32.279
...I became sensitive...

00:07:33.240 --> 00:07:33.839
...suspicious...

00:07:34.439 --> 00:07:35.319
...and domineering.

00:07:36.759 --> 00:07:39.040
I learned to hurt people in the simplest ways.

00:07:42.199 --> 00:07:43.120
But I never thought...

00:07:44.319 --> 00:07:45.800
...I'd use them all on him.

00:07:48.120 --> 00:07:49.360
I'm sorry.

00:07:50.560 --> 00:07:52.240
Being by Jiang Nanshuo's side...

00:07:52.680 --> 00:07:54.480
...must have been torture for you.

00:07:56.399 --> 00:07:57.680
Why are you apologizing?

00:07:58.040 --> 00:07:59.120
It's not your fault.

00:08:01.120 --> 00:08:02.079
Besides, all that...

00:08:03.319 --> 00:08:04.240
...is in the past.

00:08:06.079 --> 00:08:07.560
You are Weiwei...

00:08:08.439 --> 00:08:09.040
...aren't you?

00:08:15.240 --> 00:08:16.279
You are.

00:08:18.600 --> 00:08:19.759
Listen to me.

00:08:20.120 --> 00:08:21.680
Since you appeared...

00:08:22.480 --> 00:08:24.120
...you've been helping us.

00:08:25.120 --> 00:08:25.879
Once...

00:08:25.920 --> 00:08:26.800
...twice...

00:08:28.480 --> 00:08:30.199
...pushing us out of traps.

00:08:31.399 --> 00:08:32.240
You yourself...

00:08:32.559 --> 00:08:34.759
...entered the lion's den to gather evidence.

00:08:35.039 --> 00:08:37.120
You saved so many girls.

00:08:39.000 --> 00:08:39.799
If I...

00:08:41.039 --> 00:08:42.480
...rely only on intuition...

00:08:43.919 --> 00:08:45.039
...and not evidence...

00:08:47.960 --> 00:08:49.480
I'm not as good as you say.

00:08:50.519 --> 00:08:51.399
I did this...

00:08:52.080 --> 00:08:53.320
...all for myself.

00:08:56.720 --> 00:08:58.279
The gas explosion back then...

00:08:58.799 --> 00:09:00.159
...that caused the accidental fire...

00:09:01.200 --> 00:09:02.440
...allowed me to play along...

00:09:02.759 --> 00:09:03.799
...and fake my death to escape.

00:09:05.320 --> 00:09:06.759
Who I am doesn't matter anymore.

00:09:08.559 --> 00:09:09.240
I'm doing this...

00:09:09.879 --> 00:09:11.120
...for only one purpose.

00:09:12.720 --> 00:09:13.399
Revenge.

00:09:14.240 --> 00:09:15.080
I think...

00:09:17.240 --> 00:09:17.600
...you...

00:09:17.960 --> 00:09:19.399
...you are Weiwei.

00:09:20.639 --> 00:09:21.559
Even though...

00:09:22.480 --> 00:09:23.799
...your appearance has changed...

00:09:24.600 --> 00:09:25.960
...your heart hasn't.

00:09:34.639 --> 00:09:35.720
If you say so.

00:09:40.240 --> 00:09:42.240
I actually hoped you weren't.

00:09:43.519 --> 00:09:44.600
To be honest,

00:09:46.399 --> 00:09:46.879
I

00:09:48.000 --> 00:09:48.960
once suspected

00:09:49.480 --> 00:09:51.840
you were an undercover cop sent by the police.

00:09:55.080 --> 00:09:55.960
Actually,

00:09:57.240 --> 00:09:58.799
I just want to be a good person.

00:10:02.879 --> 00:10:03.799
Not funny.

00:10:05.480 --> 00:10:06.159
Cheers.

00:10:13.480 --> 00:10:15.320
Will you be like before?

00:10:16.200 --> 00:10:16.720
Although...

00:10:17.720 --> 00:10:19.679
Although I like Hei Ba,

00:10:21.159 --> 00:10:22.080
but I know

00:10:22.879 --> 00:10:24.440
what he needs is you.

00:10:28.799 --> 00:10:29.799
We can't go back.

00:10:31.120 --> 00:10:33.279
The Long Weiwei from ten years ago is long dead.

00:10:34.720 --> 00:10:35.720
I originally planned

00:10:36.399 --> 00:10:38.000
to destroy everything Jiang Nanshuo has,

00:10:39.039 --> 00:10:40.600
and then kill him with my own hands.

00:10:42.200 --> 00:10:44.080
I thought that would be the best ending.

00:10:48.360 --> 00:10:49.279
But perhaps,

00:10:49.919 --> 00:10:51.679
this is the right way now.

00:10:53.320 --> 00:10:55.240
Leaving everything to the police and the law.

00:10:58.279 --> 00:10:59.600
That Jiang Nanshuo...

00:11:01.039 --> 00:11:02.120
he simply isn't worth

00:11:02.120 --> 00:11:03.919
you sacrificing so much for him.

00:11:06.559 --> 00:11:08.039
When the dust settles,

00:11:08.480 --> 00:11:09.519
I will leave this place.

00:11:10.320 --> 00:11:11.120
To bid the past

00:11:11.279 --> 00:11:12.159
a final farewell.

00:11:14.159 --> 00:11:14.960
You're leaving?

00:11:16.039 --> 00:11:16.279
You...

00:11:16.480 --> 00:11:17.759
where are you going?

00:11:18.720 --> 00:11:19.600
Where...

00:11:20.519 --> 00:11:21.720
I don't know where yet.

00:11:25.039 --> 00:11:25.799
However,

00:11:27.559 --> 00:11:28.559
I want to hand over

00:11:28.919 --> 00:11:30.720
the remaining billiards businesses to you.

00:11:31.519 --> 00:11:32.080
But I...

00:11:32.200 --> 00:11:32.879
don't know

00:11:33.000 --> 00:11:33.960
how to do anything.

00:11:34.360 --> 00:11:34.840
And I...

00:11:34.960 --> 00:11:37.120
haven't done anything for you.

00:11:37.919 --> 00:11:38.720
I can't.

00:11:40.200 --> 00:11:40.600
You...

00:11:40.679 --> 00:11:42.960
you can find a professional to manage it.

00:11:45.759 --> 00:11:47.200
I'm not doing it for the money.

00:11:48.600 --> 00:11:49.679
I just want

00:11:50.519 --> 00:11:52.559
to let more people with pure dreams

00:11:53.399 --> 00:11:54.600
take the sport of billiards

00:11:55.240 --> 00:11:56.240
and promote and elevate it.

00:11:59.759 --> 00:12:01.759
Just like Cheng Ye ten years ago.

00:12:03.399 --> 00:12:05.200
Then what about Hei Ba?

00:12:07.080 --> 00:12:08.200
To me, he is

00:12:09.799 --> 00:12:11.000
both salvation

00:12:13.320 --> 00:12:14.440
and trauma.

00:12:19.639 --> 00:12:20.720
And for him...

00:12:23.360 --> 00:12:24.399
even without me,

00:12:25.720 --> 00:12:26.840
he will continue to love

00:12:26.840 --> 00:12:28.039
the sport of billiards.

00:12:32.679 --> 00:12:34.240
I can't bear to let you go.

00:12:34.759 --> 00:12:35.320
We

00:12:35.519 --> 00:12:37.399
just became friends.

00:12:39.679 --> 00:12:40.639
In my heart,

00:12:41.320 --> 00:12:42.639
you've been a friend for a long time.

00:12:43.600 --> 00:12:44.519
Weiwei...

00:12:46.120 --> 00:12:48.720
I think I've become your fan.